@node BALAN "Balance of Power"

@{b}Balance of Power@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = PT(R)
Type    = Sorcery
Cost    = 3UU
Artist  = Adam Rex

Text(PT): If you have Fewer cards in your hand than your opponent does,
          draw until you have the same number. (When you play Balance
          of Power, it doesn`t count as in your hand.)

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}
